OL,3,CRory McIlroy plans to keep his foot on
OL,4,Cthe gas after surging clear at Augusta
OL,6,FDefending champion Rory McIlroy plans
OL,7,Fto carry on swinging and keep "his
OL,8,Ffoot on the gas" rather than trying to
OL,9,Fprotect a record-breaking 36-hole
OL,10,FMasters lead.
OL,12,FSix birdies in his last seven holes
OL,13,Fsaw the Northern Irishman post a 65
OL,14,Fand a 12-under-par total, his six-
OL,15,Fstroke halfway advantage the best in
OL,16,Fthe tournament's history.
OL,26,@oD@_OUpD@PO]
