OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1775927152
OL,3,CRory McIlroy plans to keep his foot on
OL,4,Cthe gas after surging clear at Augusta
OL,6,FMcIlroy has memories, albeit distant
OL,7,Fnow, of losing a four-shot lead on the
OL,8,Ffinal day of the 2011 Masters but he
OL,9,Fbounced back two months later by
OL,10,Fmaintaining an eight-shot 56-hole
OL,11,Fadvantage to win the US Open.
OL,13,F"I've built up a nice cushion at this
OL,14,Fpoint. I guess my mindset is just
OL,15,Ftrying to keep playing well and
OL,16,Fkeeping my foot on the gas," said the
OL,17,Fworld number two, whose bid to become
OL,18,Fonly the fourth man to win back-to-
OL,19,Fback green jackets is well on track.
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1775927152
OL,3,CRory McIlroy plans to keep his foot on
OL,4,Cthe gas after surging clear at Augusta
OL,6,F"Don't protect it. Go out and play
OL,7,Ffreely, keep swinging. A big part of
OL,8,Fthe lesson from the 2011 Masters to
OL,9,Fthe 2011 US Open was don't get
OL,10,Fprotective.
OL,12,F"Go out there and keep playing, keep
OL,13,Ftrying to make birdies, stay as
OL,14,Ftrusting and as committed as possible."
OL,16,FIf McIlroy wanted to send out a
OL,17,Fmessage to his rivals ` the closest
OL,18,Fbeing 2018 champion Patrick Reed and
OL,19,FSam Burns ` it was the way he turned
OL,20,Fup the heat on the back nine in a
OL,21,Fdominant display.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
