OL,3,CRory McIlroy plans to keep his foot on
OL,4,Cthe gas after surging clear at Augusta
OL,6,FHowever, he rejected the suggestion
OL,7,Fthat in this mood he intimidated
OL,8,Fopponents.
OL,10,F"No. That's not me, that's not what I
OL,11,Fwant to do. Honestly, I don't care,"
OL,12,Fhe added.
OL,14,FOn the eve of the tournament McIlroy
OL,15,Fhad said, considering the hard and
OL,16,Ffast conditions, double digits under
OL,17,Fpar "would be an amazing score". He
OL,18,Fwas referring to Sunday.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@dO]yD@EOUyD@_O]
