OL,3,CRory McIlroy plans to keep his foot on
OL,4,Cthe gas after surging clear at Augusta
OL,6,FIn that respect he is two days ahead
OL,7,Fof schedule but light years ahead of a
OL,8,Fstacked leaderboard which had four
OL,9,Fother major winners trailing in his
OL,10,Fwake.
OL,12,FAfter reeling off three successive
OL,13,Fbirdies from the second to get to
OL,14,Feight under he responded to two bogeys
OL,15,Fmid-round with five birdies in six
OL,16,Fholes from the 12th.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
