OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1775927152
OL,3,CRory McIlroy plans to keep his foot on
OL,4,Cthe gas after surging clear at Augusta
OL,6,FThat dubious honour went to Burns, who
OL,7,Ffinished with three birdies in his
OL,8,Flast four holes much earlier in the
OL,9,Fday for a 71.
OL,11,FJustin Rose was five under after four
OL,12,Fbirdies in five holes from the seventh
OL,13,Fboosted a round that was going nowhere.
OL,15,FThe Englishman said last year's near
OL,16,Fmiss in a play-off had no bearing on
OL,17,Fhis current approach.
OL,19,F"Of course I want to win this
OL,20,Ftournament. I don't really need to try
OL,21,Fany harder," he said.
OL,26,@{D@AOU}D@LO]
