OL,3,CRory McIlroy plans to keep his foot on
OL,4,Cthe gas after surging clear at Augusta
OL,6,FRyder Cup team-mate Shane Lowry joined
OL,7,Fhim on that score after a 69, with the
OL,8,FIrishman saying; "If you gave me this
OL,9,Fposition yesterday morning I would
OL,10,Fhave taken your hand off."
OL,12,FBut at seven shots back, and with
OL,13,FMcIlroy in such commanding form,
OL,14,FFleetwood admitted they were already
OL,15,Fup against it.
OL,17,F"Rory has a pretty commanding lead, in
OL,18,Fwhich case it's up to him what
OL,19,Fhappens," he said.
OL,26,@pD@ROUrD@ZO]yD@AOU{D@IO]
